  "description": "Gothic font resource pack. Spice up your medival themed worlds with this dark fantasy feeling font.",
  "body": "# 𝔉𝔯𝔞𝔨𝔱𝔲𝔯\n![Icon](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PPt77SS0/bf588581ae824015b14d288464c0ca79105f1155_96.webp 'Icon') [![TLOTD Icon](https://tlotd.net/minecraft/mod/tlotd-made.png)](https://tlotd.net) [![Isla_Nublar Icon](https://tlotd.net/minecraft/mod/isla_nublar_made.png)](https://isla-nublar.com)\n\n*\"Gothic text resource pack. Spice up your medival themed worlds with this dark fantasy feeling font.\"*\n\n# About\n\nThis is a resource pack that changes the vanilla font to a slightly edited version of Jacquard 12, a font originally created by Sarah Cadigan-Fried and adapted for use in Minecraft. This was portet to a bitmap font by me and supports all letters of the Germanic Languages aswell as Spanish, Polish, Hungarian and Romanian alphabets at the moment. This should work with any version since Minecarft 1.20.",
